    "causal_summary": "Our review skills (sk-code-review, deep-review) emit free-form verdicts that are unreliable to parse via regex or NLP. sk-code-review SKILL.md:308 produces \"APPROVE / REQUEST_CHANGES / COMMENT\" in prose; deep-review SKILL.md:367-372 produces \"FAIL/CONDITIONAL/PASS\" embedded in synthesis text. CI bots, PR status checks, and automation scripts cannot reliably extract review status without ad-hoc regex that breaks on prose variation.",
